(129, 'Netgear JGS516PE 16 Port Gigabit Smart Managed Plus Switch (8 Port PoE)', 'admin', 9, 95, 42, '255', '255', 'youtube', NULL, 'Switch', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Netgear JGS516PE 16-port Gigabit Ethernet switch with 8 PoE ports (802.3af) providing up to 15w per port with 85w total PoE power budget. ESSENTIAL NETWORKING - Segment and prioritize your traffic with VLAN, QoS, IGMP Snooping, rate limiting and traffic monitoring. Monitor your network status and your cabling with the port statistics and cable health. DESKTOP / 1U Rack mountable form factor. Jumbo frame support. 16 Gigabit Ethernet ports deliver up to 2000 Mbps of dedicated, non-blocking bandwidth per port</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Netgear JGS516PE\r\n</p><p>Gigabit Ports 16 Port\r\n</p><p>Buffer size 6Mb or 768KB\r\n</p><p>100-240V, 50-60Hz, 1.5A max\r\n</p><p>MTBF 840,354</p>', 12100.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.05', 5, 1, 1200.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'netgerar price in bd', 'netgerar price in bd', '255', NULL, 'netgear-jgs516pe-16-port-gigabit-smart-managed-plus-switch-8-port-poe-yij8u', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-25 18:08:12', '2021-11-29 12:36:04'),
(130, 'Mikrotik CSS326-24G-2S+RM SwOS powered 24 port Gigabit Ethernet switch with two SFP+ ports in 1U rackmount case', 'admin', 9, 96, 46, '256', '256', 'youtube', NULL, 'Swtich', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Mikrotik CSS326-24G-2S+RM SwOS powered 24 port Gigabit Ethernet switch with two SFP+ ports in 1U rackmount case\r\n</p><p>Cloud Smart Switch 326-24G-2S+RM is SwOS powered 24 port Gigabit Ethernet switch with two SFP+ ports in 1U rackmount case that provides wire speed connectivity with several new switching features.\r\n</p><p>It gives you all the basic functionality for a managed switch, plus more: allows to manage port-to-port forwarding, apply MAC filter, configure VLANs, mirror traffic, apply bandwidth limitation and even adjust some MAC and IP header fields. SFP cage supports both 1.25 Gb SFP and 10 Gb SFP+ modules.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Mikrotik CSS326-24G-2S+RM\r\n</p><p>Dimensions: 440 x 144 x 44 mm\r\n</p><p>Storage size: 2 MB\r\n</p><p>Storage type: FLASH</p>', 15290.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '1.0', 5, 1, 1340.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'Mikrotik price in bd', 'Mikrotik price in bd', '256', NULL, 'mikrotik-css326-24g-2srm-swos-powered-24-port-gigabit-ethernet-switch-with-two-sfp-ports-in-1u-rackmount-case-qzkgb', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-25 18:14:14', '2021-11-29 12:49:16'),
(131, 'D-Link DGS-1008MP 8 port 10/100/1000 Giga Unmanaged PoE Desktop Switch', 'admin', 9, 94, 48, '258', '258', 'youtube', NULL, 'Switch', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-Link DGS-1008MP 8 port 10/100/1000 Giga Unmanaged PoE Desktop Switch\r\n</p><p>This compact beauty offers PoE to 802.3af/at standard across all eight Gigabit Ethernet ports, at up to 30 Watts per port with a power budget total of 125 Watts. This, put simply, means you can power devices such as access points, IP phones and video surveillance cameras simply by plugging them in with an Ethernet cable – no additional power required. The DGS-1008MP features 8 x 10/100/1000BASE-T ports that support the IEEE 802.3at PoE+ protocol. Each of the 8 PoE+ ports can supply up to 30 watts with a total PoE power budget of 125 watts. PoE is especially suitable for devices that are far from power outlets or when you want to minimise the clutter of extra cables. No configuration is required and installation is quick and easy. Support for Auto MDI/MDI-X on all ports eliminates the need for crossover cables when connecting to another switch. Auto- Negotiation on each port senses the link speed of a network device (10, 100 or 1000 Mbps) and intelligently adjusts for compatibility and optimal performance. The switch has been designed without fans ensuring silent operation wherever it is installed. With wire-speed filtering and store-and-forward switching, the DGS-1008MP maximises network performance while minimising the transmission of bad network packets. No configuration is required and installation is quick and easy. Support for Auto MDI/MDI-X on all ports eliminates the need for crossover cables when connecting to another switch. Auto- Negotiation on each port senses the link speed of a network device (10, 100 or 1000 Mbps) and intelligently adjusts for compatibility and optimal performance. The switch has been designed without fans ensuring silent operation wherever it is installed. With wire-speed filtering and store-and-forward switching, the DGS-1008MP maximises network performance while minimising the transmission of bad network packets. DGS-1008MP switches feature both D-Link Green 3.0 Technology and IEEE802.3az Energy Efficient Ethernet (EEE) to cut operating costs without sacrificing operational performance or functionality. With D-Link Green technology, the switches constantly monitor the link status and network utilisation of every port. The switches also automatically detect cable length and can reduce transmission power usage for shorter cables. By pairing EEE capable devices with DGS-1008MP switches organizations can drastically reduce power consumption by automatically putting ports into a sleep mode when not being used.\r\n</p><p>01 Year Warranty.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: D-Link DGS-1008MP\r\n</p><p>Connect More PoE Devices\r\n</p><p>PoE+ Support with High Power Budget\r\n</p><p>Gigabit Ethernet Speed</p>', 7260.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.5', 5, 1, 680.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'D-Link price in bd', 'D-Link price in bd', '258', NULL, 'd-link-dgs-1008mp-8-port-101001000-giga-unmanaged-poe-desktop-switch-e30nt', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-25 18:25:02', '2021-11-29 12:07:04'),
(132, 'Netgear GS116LP 16-Port Gigabit Ethernet Rackmount Unmanaged PoE/PoE+ Switch', 'admin', 9, 95, 42, '259', '259', 'youtube', NULL, 'Switch', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Netgear GS116LP 16-Port Gigabit Ethernet Rackmount Unmanaged PoE/PoE+ Switch\r\n</p><p>The 16-Port Gigabit Ethernet PoE+ Unmanaged Switch from NETGEAR allows you to connect your network with up to 16 Ethernet-enabled devices. This unmanaged switch comes equipped with 16 Gigabit Ethernet PoE+ ports offering 32 Gb/s network connectivity along with a total PoE power budget of 76W. Additionally, it supports 802.1p and DSCP-based QoS functionality to ensure bandwidth-intensive applications receive the necessary network resources to function smoothly. The unit also supports 802.3az Energy Efficient Ethernet which adjusts power according to network traffic and cable length. The standards-based Gigabit switches to sense and adjusts for network speed and cabling type automatically. It integrates into your existing Ethernet network, whether it is running at 10/100 Mb/s or Gigabit speed. Simple set up with no software or configuration needed. Front-panel LEDs keep you informed of power status, link speed, and link activities. Supports the Energy Efficient Ethernet (IEEE 802.3az) standard, which reduces energy consumption when there is light traffic on an active port or when there is no link or no activity detected.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Netgear GS116LP 16-Port\r\n</p><p>16 x Gigabit Ethernet PoE+ Ports\r\n</p><p>32 Gb/s Bandwidth\r\n</p><p>Store-and-Forward Support\r\n</p><p>76W Total PoE Power Budget</p>', 14850.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '1.0', 5, 1, 1400.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'netgerar price in bd', 'netgerar price in bd', '259', NULL, 'netgear-gs116lp-16-port-gigabit-ethernet-rackmount-unmanaged-poepoe-switch-89vqn', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-25 18:30:44', '2021-11-29 12:34:40'),
(133, 'TP-Link LS1005 5-Port 10/100Mbps Desktop Network Switch', 'admin', 9, 93, 47, '260', '260', 'youtube', NULL, 'Swtich', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP-Link LS1005 5-Port 10/100Mbps Desktop Network Switch\r\n</p><p>The TP-Link LS1005 5-Port 10/100Mbps Desktop Network Switch is equipped with 5-gigabit RJ45 ports. It is easy to use and reliable. With these plug-and-play switches, you can expand your network connections to multiple devices instantly. With all ports supporting Auto-MDI/MDIX, there’s no need to worry about the type of cable to use. It also supports energy-efficient technology, helping you save power and money. Power consumption automatically adjusts according to the link status and cable length, allowing you to expand your network while minimizing your carbon footprint. Save the planet and lower your energy bills. It has a compact desktop design, to meet your needs in any environment. Besides, the fanless design ensures quiet operation. The LS1005 is fully compatible with networked devices such as computers, printers, webcams, IPTVs. It has a wide range of application scenarios and is suitable for networking in school dormitories, surveillance, homes, and small businesses. The TP-Link LS1005 comes with 01 years of warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: LS1005\r\n</p><p>5× 10/100Mbos Auto-Negotiation RJ45 ports\r\n</p><p>Green Ethernet technology\r\n</p><p>IEEE 802.3X flow control\r\n</p><p>Plastic casing and desktop design</p>', 600.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.5', 5, 1, 60.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '260', NULL, 'tp-link-ls1005-5-port-10100mbps-desktop-network-switch-lkuc6', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 00:50:44', '2021-11-29 11:44:01'),
(134, 'D-Link DES-1008P 8-Port Desktop Switch with 4 PoE Ports', 'admin', 9, 94, 48, '261', '261', 'youtube', NULL, 'Switch', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-Link DES-1008P 8-Port Desktop Switch with 4 PoE Ports\r\n</p><p>D-Link DES-1008P 8-Port Desktop Switchcomes with 4 PoE Ports. This Desktop Switch featured with Eight 10/100 Mbps Fast Ethernet ports, Full/half-duplex for Ethernet/Fast Ethernet speeds, IEEE 802.3x ﬂow control, Store-and-forward switching scheme, RoHS compliant, Plug-and-play installation, Auto MDI/MDIX crossover for all ports and Compact lightweight chassis. It can be used to share files, music and video across your network or create a multi-player gaming environment. The Desktop Switch runs ultra-quiet, making it ideal for both home and small office use.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: DES-1008P\r\n</p><p>Full/half-duplex for Ethernet/Fast Ethernet speeds\r\n</p><p>8 x 10/100 Mbps Fast Ethernet ports\r\n</p><p>IEEE 802.3x ﬂow control\r\n</p><p>Store and Forward switching scheme</p>', 4050.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.05', 5, 1, 395.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'D-Link price in bd', 'D-Link price in bd', '261', NULL, 'd-link-des-1008p-8-port-desktop-switch-with-4-poe-ports-c6m1m', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 00:58:10', '2021-11-29 12:06:04'),
(135, 'D-Link DES-1016A-16-port 10/100M Unmanaged Switch', 'admin', 9, 94, 48, '262', '262', 'youtube', NULL, 'Switch', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-Link DES-1016A-16-port 10/100M Unmanaged Switch\r\n</p><p>The D-Link DES-1016A 16-Port 10/100 Switch is part of D-Link’s new series of SOHO devices that make use of D-Link’s Green Technology, providing energy savings, reduced heat, and a longer product life without sacrificing performance or functionality. An energy-efficient power adapter (Energy Star Level V qualified), minimized use of harmful substances (RoHS compliant), and recyclable packaging make this switch truly environmentally friendly.\r\n</p><p>Warranty - 01 Year</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: DES-1016A\r\n</p><p>Interface: 16 10/100 Mbps LAN\r\n</p><p>Dimensions: 280 x 125.8 x 44 mm\r\n</p><p>MAC Add: 8K entries per device</p>', 1950.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.5', 5, 1, 200.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'D-Link price in bd', 'D-Link price in bd', '262', NULL, 'd-link-des-1016a-16-port-10100m-unmanaged-switch-o3rk9', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 01:05:16', '2021-11-29 12:04:56'),
