(150, 'TP Link Archer A9 AC1900 Wireless MU-MIMO Gigabit Router', 'admin', 9, 81, 47, '280', '280', 'youtube', NULL, 'Router', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP Link Archer A9 AC1900 Wireless MU-MIMO Gigabit Router\r\n</p><p>Archer A9 delivers WiFi speeds of up to 1300 Mbps on the 5 GHz band and 600 Mbps on the 2.4 GHz band. Handle simple tasks like sending e-mails or web browsing with the 2.4 GHz band and bandwidth-intensive tasks like online gaming or HD streaming with the 5 GHz band—simultaneously. Three external antennas and one internal antenna sends WiFi signals to every corner of your home. Beamforming technology detects devices, even if they are far-away or low-powered, and concentrates wireless signal strength towards them. Archer A9 helps your devices achieve optimal performance by making communication more efficient with MU-MIMO technology. Three simultaneous data streams allow all connected devices to achieve speeds up to 3× faster than standard AC routers. Smart Connect helps the router automatically switch each device\'s connection to the best available WiFi band while Airtime Fairness prevents older devices from slowing down your network. With both working together, everyone can enjoy a smoother WiFi experience without lag. Archer A9 improves your online safety and security by providing advanced features and technology like Parental Controls, Access Control and a VPN Server. You can also benefit from the very latest security enhancements—WPA3 if you keep your router\'s firmware up to date. Gigabit Ethernet ports (1 WAN + 4 LAN) deliver maximum wired speeds. Plug in your PCs, smart TVs and game consoles for fast and reliable connections. Set up Archer A9 in minutes via its intuitive web interface or the Tether app. Tether also lets you manage network settings including parental controls and media sharing from any Android or iOS device.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TP Link Archer A9 AC1900\r\n</p><p>802.11ac Wave2 Wi-Fi\r\n</p><p>MU-MIMO Technology\r\n</p><p>Boosted WiFi Coverage\r\n</p><p>1 Year Warranty</p>', 8100.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '.05', 5, 1, 800.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '280', NULL, 'TP-Link-Archer-A9-AC1900-Wireless-MU-MIMO-Gigabit-Router-DC3yR', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 11:37:24', '2021-11-26 11:37:24'),
(151, 'TP-Link Archer AX6000 6000mbps 8 Antenna Dual-Band Next-Gen Wi-Fi 6 Gigabit Router', 'admin', 9, 83, 47, '281', '281', 'youtube', NULL, 'Router', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP-Link Archer AX6000 6000mbps 8 Antenna Dual-Band Next-Gen Wi-Fi 6 Gigabit Router\r\n</p><p>Fast, High Efficiency\r\n</p><p>Gaming, 4K/8K streaming, smart home devices, and AR/VR all compete for network resources, creating lag and crowding your network. To solve this problem, 802.11ax5 (also known as Wi-Fi 6), a next-gen high-efficiency WiFi standard, was created. Now, you can simultaneously connect more devices1 and enjoy the optimum speed for each of them.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TP-Link Archer AX6000 802.11AX\r\n</p><p>Speed: 1148 Mbps at 2.4 GHz + 4804 Mbps at 5 GHz\r\n</p><p>4x Larger Capacity\r\n</p><p>Lightning-Fast Connections\r\n</p><p>8 high-gain external antennas</p>', 27830.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '0.5', 5, 1, 2550.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '281', NULL, 'tp-link-archer-ax6000-6000mbps-8-antenna-dual-band-next-gen-wi-fi-6-gigabit-router-1uhsx', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 11:42:08', '2021-11-26 13:45:02'),
(152, 'TP-Link Deco M4 (3 Pack) Whole Home Mesh Wi-Fi System AC1200 Dual-band Router', 'admin', 9, 83, 47, '282', '282', 'youtube', NULL, 'Router', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP-Link Deco M4 (3 Pack) Whole Home Mesh Wi-Fi System AC1200 Dual-band Router\r\n</p><p>TP-Link Deco M4 is the simplest way to guarantee a strong Wi-Fi signal in every corner of your home up to 5500 square feet (3-pack). This router has a feature called Mesh. It means Deco units work together to form one unified network. Your phone or tablet automatically connects to the fastest Deco as you move through your home, creating a truly seamless Wi-Fi experience. Network speeds three times faster than previous generation routers, thanks to 802.11ac wireless technology, make Deco capable of providing a lag-free connection to up to 100 devices .It has Multiple 2-in-1 Router and Access Point Modes. Installing Deco M4 is fast and easy. Just unpack the system, download the Deco app and follow its onscreen directions. Pair with Alexa to control Deco M4 with simple voice commands. Enjoy the convenient life.\r\n</p><p>This router comes with 01 year warranty service.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TP-Link Deco M4\r\n</p><p>Deliver Wi-Fi to an area of up to 4,000 square feet\r\n</p><p>connect up to 100 devices\r\n</p><p>Frequency: 2.4 GHz, 5 GHz\r\n</p><p>Speed up to 1200 Mbps</p>', 14850.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '0.5', 5, 1, 1360.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '282', NULL, 'tp-link-deco-m4-3-pack-whole-home-mesh-wi-fi-system-ac1200-dual-band-router-njnww', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 11:46:23', '2021-11-26 13:44:31'),
(153, 'TP-Link Deco X60 AX3000 Wi-Fi 6 Mesh Router (3-pack)', 'admin', 9, 83, 47, '283', '283', 'youtube', NULL, 'Router', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP-Link Deco X60 AX3000 Wi-Fi 6 Mesh Router (3-pack)\r\n</p><p>Game-Changer: Wi-Fi 6 Mesh\r\n</p><p>Armed with Wi-Fi 6 technology, Deco whole home mesh Wi-Fi is designed to deliver a huge boost in coverage, speed, and total capacity. Get on the latest mesh Wi-Fi to enjoy the future network that loads faster and connects more. Deco X60 builds a more efficient network with 4× the average throughput on connected devices in dense environments thanks to Wi-Fi 6 technology.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TP-Link Deco X60\r\n</p><p>SPEED: 574 Mbps at 2.4 GHz + 2402 Mbps at 5 GHz\r\n</p><p>6 Streams\r\n</p><p>Seamless Roaming\r\n</p><p>4× Internal Antennas</p>', 34980.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '0.5', 5, 1, 3200.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '283', NULL, 'tp-link-deco-x60-ax3000-wi-fi-6-mesh-router-3-pack-ygg0x', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 11:49:37', '2021-11-26 13:43:37'),
(154, 'TP-Link TL-WR844N 300 Mbps Multi-Mode Wi-Fi Router', 'admin', 9, 83, 47, '284', '284', 'youtube', NULL, 'Router', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>TP-Link TL-WR844N 300 Mbps Multi-Mode Wi-Fi Router\r\n</p><p>Enjoy web browsing, HD streaming, and downloading with your family. 300 Mbps wireless speeds on the 2.4 GHz band meet your daily needs. Enhance wireless signal transmission with two 5 dBi antennas, 2×2 MIMO technology, and five high-speed Ethernet ports to provide reliable Wi-Fi and wired connections throughout medium-sized homes. Easily manage your home network with versatile built-in tools, including Parental Controls, Guest Network, QoS, and more. Plug in an Ethernet cable to instantly create a private wireless network and share internet access with all your Wi-Fi devices. Transform your existing wired network into a wireless one. Boost the existing wireless coverage in your house. Connect to the ISP network wirelessly in areas without wired service. IGMP Proxy/Snooping, Bridge, and Tag VLAN support optimizes IPTV streaming so you can enjoy your favorite movies and shows lag-free. Compatible with the most recent Internet Protocol version (IPv6). Keep your router future-proof and enjoy the IPv6 services provided by your ISP. Designed to conserve space and complement virtually any décor while delivering stable Wi-Fi to your home.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TP-Link TL-WR844N 300 Mbps\r\n</p><p>Speed: 300 Mbps at 2.4 GHz\r\n</p><p>2× Antennas\r\n</p><p>High-Speed Wi-Fi\r\n</p><p>Versatile Management\r\n</p><p>View More Info</p>', 1400.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '0.5', 5, 1, 75.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, 0, 'TP-Link price in bd', 'TP-Link price in bd', '284', NULL, 'tp-link-tl-wr844n-300-mbps-multi-mode-wi-fi-router-6vmw4', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-26 11:52:38', '2021-11-26 13:43:00'),
