(269, 'FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine', 'admin', 9, 135, 74, '402', '402', 'youtube', NULL, 'Splicer Machine', '<p>FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine is an Active Alignment (DAA: Digitalized Active Alignment) splicer machine. The machine has an average loss of SM(0.02dB) / MM(0.01dB) / DS(0.05dB) / NZDS(0.05dB) / G.657(0.02dB) with a splicing time of 12s average SM / SM 7s Quick mode. It has 78+ 8 user modes, User installable mode : 70+ splicing programs with attenuation range of 0.1dB ~ 20dB (0.1dB step). The fiber types that can be used in this machine are SM(ITU-T G.652, MM(ITU-T G.651), DS(ITU-T G.653), NZDS(ITU-T G.655), IT-G657A, IT-G657B, 0.25mm, 0.9mm, 2.0mm, 2.4mm, 3.0mm, FLAT(indoor cable). The average heating time is 18 second and there are 26 (Factory installed mode : 3, User installable mode : 23) heating modes that are available. The machine can store up to 2000 records. To detect the fiber, the machine uses 2 CCD camera system with Color 4.3\" LCD monitor, with Touch Screen (Tempered Glass) monitor which allows you to see all the functions and features clearly. The battery used here typical 200 Cycles (Splice &amp; Heat) / single battery &lt;2 Batteries Standard&gt; with a power supply ability of AC 100-240V input or DC 9~14V. The max wind speed resistance of this splicer machine is 15m/s.\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine has 1 Year Warranty.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: FiberFox Mini 4S+\r\n</p><p>Smallest and the Lightest Active Alignment Fiber Fusion Splicer\r\n</p><p>SOC Compatible\r\n</p><p>Stability and Splicing Performance\r\n</p><p>Waterproof, Anti-shock, Dustproof</p>', 214500.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '1.0', 1, 1, 19800.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'Splicer Machine price in bd', 'Splicer Machine price in bd', '402',