(270, 'AC Net F-95 Optical Fiber ARC Fusion Splicer Machine', 'admin', 9, 135, 73, '403', '403', 'youtube', NULL, 'Splicer Matchine', '<p>AC Net F-95 Optical Fiber ARC Fusion Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The AC-Net F-95 optical fiber splicer machine has a 100% true loss report display after splicing, supports FTTH and cable TV digital system, 7800 mAh battery provides 400 nos splicing, high performance and low maintenance, suitable for rough conditions in Bangladesh. It has a 1-year warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: F-95\r\n</p><p>100% true loss report display after splicing\r\n</p><p>Supports FTTH and cable TV digital system\r\n</p><p>Splicing Capacity: 400 Nos Splicing\r\n</p><p>7800 mAh battery</p>', 120500.00, NULL, 0, '[]', '[]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 'quantity', 1, 0, 0, 0, '1.5', 1, 1, 11200.00, 'amount', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'Splicer Machine price in bd', 'Splicer Machine price in bd', '403', NULL, 'AC-Net-F-95-Optical-Fiber-ARC-Fusion-Splicer-Machine-wSdLK', 0.00, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2021-11-28 12:43:43', '2021-11-28 12:43:43'),
