(237, 247, 'Ugreen RJ45 Cat 6 Shielding Crystal Connector 10 Pcs (1Pack) #20333', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Ugreen RJ45 Cat 6 Shielding Crystal Connector 10 Pcs (1Pack) #20333\r\n</p><p>UGREEN network connector offers RJ45 Crimp Connectors for CAT5E, CAT5 Network Cable, which is perfect for building custom-length network cables. With STP 8P8C 50 micron Gold Plated Connectors, the ethernet connectors achieve better data transmitting. The network connector applier to max cable jacket OD is 0.26 inches (6.5mm) and max conductor OD is 0.039 inches (1mm). Package includes 10 pieces Gold plated leads RJ45 Modular Plug Network Connector for UTP, Cat5, Cat5e, Solid/Stranded Network Cable Heads.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: 20333\r\n</p><p>Model: Ugreen RJ45 Cat 6 10 Pcs\r\n</p><p>Package includes 10 Pieces of RJ45 Modular Plug Network Connector\r\n</p><p>Better Data Transfer\r\n</p><p>Material: Clear Plastic</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:10:10', '2021-11-28 11:10:10'),
(238, 248, 'Ugreen RJ45 Cat6 FTP Modular Plugs Shielding Crystal Head 100 Pcs (1Pack) #50248', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Ugreen RJ45 Cat6 FTP Modular Plugs Shielding Crystal Head 100 Pcs (1Pack) #50248\r\n</p><p>Ugreen 50248 is RJ45 Cat6 FTP Modular Plugs Shielding Crystal Head. Here Include 100 ethernet connectors in the package, which perfectly meets the daily demands. Its 24k gold-plated design provides maximum conductivity and durability and gives superior protection on the product interior. This Shieled RJ45 Crimp Connectors for CAT5E, CAT5 Network Cable, STP 8P8C 50 micron Gold Plating Connectors for better data transmitting. In this Shielding Crystal Connector, Max cable jacket OD is 0.26 inches and max conductor OD is 0.40 inches and also Max cable jacket OD is 0.26 inches, and max conductor OD is 0.40 inches. The Network Connector is compatible with Cat5 Cat5e and Cat5 Ethernet cable. This new Ugreen RJ45 Cat6 FTP Modular plug has 01-year warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: 50248\r\n</p><p>Model: RJ45 Cat6 FTP\r\n</p><p>Cat-6 Shielding Crystal Head\r\n</p><p>RJ45 network adapter\r\n</p><p>Compatible: RJ45 cat6, cat6e\r\n</p><p>24K gold plated</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:14:40', '2021-11-28 11:14:40'),
(239, 249, 'Micronet Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector-Pack Of 20 Pieces', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Micronet Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector-Pack Of 20 Pieces\r\n</p><p>Micronet high-quality RJ45 plugs, SP1113, are perfect for use with 10Base-T, 100Base-T, and Gigabit Ethernet network environment. \r\n</p><p>The plug maintains high bandwidth and maximum data signal with its connection cables. \r\n</p><p>SP1113 is also designed in snag-less moldings for easy installation, so that the user can quickly configure it with its belonging cable into straight-through or cross-over cable with the minimum workforce and reduce much of network infrastructure building time</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Micronet Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector\r\n</p><p>Micronet high-quality RJ45 plugs\r\n</p><p>Gigabit Ethernet network\r\n</p><p>Plug maintains high bandwidth</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:17:57', '2021-11-28 11:17:57'),
(240, 250, 'AMP Cat-6 Connector of Full Box (100 Unit Per Box)', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>AMP Cat-6 Connector of Full Box (100 Unit Per Box)\r\n</p><p>Plug Type RJ-45\r\n</p><p>Conductors 8\r\n</p><p>material 3U Golden Cooper\r\n</p><p>Connector RJ45 Female Connector\r\n</p><p>closure material PC\r\n</p><p>Connector type RJ45\r\n</p><p>Keywords Modular Jack Connector</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: AMP Cat-6\r\n</p><p>Plug Type RJ-45\r\n</p><p>Conductors 8\r\n</p><p>material 3U Golden Cooper</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:21:15', '2021-11-28 11:21:15'),
(241, 251, 'D-Link Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector - Pack Of 100 Pieces (Original)', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-Link Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector - Pack Of 100 Pieces (Original)\r\n</p><p>RJ45 modular plug supports 4 twisted pairs, meet wiring scheme \r\n</p><p>Housing: polycarbonate, 94V-2, transparent color \r\n</p><p>Contact terminal: phosphor bronze \r\n</p><p>Finished: 50 micro-inch gold plating, over 50 micro inch Nickel plated on contact area \r\n</p><p>Operating temperature: -40°C to 80°C \r\n</p><p>Cable to plug tensile strength: 7.7 kgs \r\n</p><p>Terminates 24-26 AWG stranded wires, wiring scheme T568A/T568B</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: D-Link Cat 6 RJ45 Cable Connector\r\n</p><p>Polycarbonate, 94V-2\r\n</p><p>50 micro-inch gold plating\r\n</p><p>50 micro inch Nickel plated</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:24:21', '2021-11-28 11:24:21'),
(242, 252, 'Ugreen Cat6 UTP Flat 3M Ethernet Cable #50186', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Ugreen Cat6 UTP Flat 3M Ethernet Cable #50186\r\n</p><p>Ugreen 50186 is one klind of Cat6 UTP Flat 3M Ethernet Cable. This is Prefabricated network cable is the ideal cable to connect devices in your network together. The Ugreen 50186 network cable is made of pure PVC, corrosion-resistant, Bare copper, provides durability, and ensures a safe connection; Bare copper conductor enhances cable performance and complies with the specifications for communication cables. This Cat6 cable support network speed 10/100/1000 Mbps, operating frequency up to 250MHz, cable. the cable is Made of pure copper core (CU) and 24k gold-plated contact pins, the cross-noise reduction core provides stable and durable signal transmission over long periods of use. With the ability to transmit LAN signals at high speed. Its Advanced stable design and production line designed with international standard high-grade raw materials.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: 50186\r\n</p><p>Model: Cat6 UTP Flat\r\n</p><p>Good connection to 10, 100,1000 Base-T networks\r\n</p><p>Cable Conductor Material: Bare copper\r\n</p><p>Anti-tangle flat cable, Length: 3m\r\n</p><p>Cable Performance: up to 500 MHz</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:28:14', '2021-11-28 11:28:14'),
(243, 253, 'D-Link Cat-6 UTP Networking Cable (China)-305 Meter Per Box', '1.0', '<p>Specification:\r\n</p><p>Category : 6 UTP Solid cable\r\n</p><p>Insulation Material : HD-PE\r\n</p><p>OD : 6mm ±0.2\r\n</p><p>Jacket hardness : 45P (90A ± 2A, Shore)\r\n</p><p>Heat-resistant : 75 degree C minimum (Temperature limited)</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: D-Link CAT.6 UTP Cable 305M\r\n</p><p>PE insulation\r\n</p><p>PE central cross\r\n</p><p>FR PVC/LSZH Jacket</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:31:52', '2021-11-28 11:31:52'),
(244, 254, 'Ugreen Cat 6 Pure Copper 0.5 M Flat LAN Cable #50183', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Ugreen Cat 6 Pure Copper 0.5 M Flat LAN Cable #50183\r\n</p><p>The new Ugreen Cat6 cable is the ideal cable to connect devices in network together, It supporting 10/100/1000 Mbps network speed, operating frequency up to 250MHz, It is also featured with pure copper core (CU) and 24k gold-plated contact pins, the core reduces cross interference to provide stable and durable signal transmission over long periods of use. This new Ugreen network cable is made of pure PVC, corrosion resistant, provides durability, and ensures a secure connection; bare copper conductor enhances cable performance and complies with specifications for communications cables. It is also comes with slim profile convenient for wiring. With LAN signal transmission speed with height, stability. Design and manufacture on advanced lines with high-class input materials of international standards. The Cat6 UTP Lan flat cable is a cable standard for Gigabit Ethernet and other network protocols. This cable provides performance of up to 500 MHz and is suitable for 10BASE-T, 100 BASE-TX (Fast Ethernet), 1000 BASE-T / 1000 BASE-TX (Gigabit Ethernet) and 10 GB ASE-T (10-Gigabit Ethernet). And it’s designed for use on Ethernet / RJ45 networks. And Suitable for connecting your PC, Xbox, PS3, Laptop to your broadband router.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: 50183\r\n</p><p>Model: Ugreen Cat 6 Copper 50cm LAN Cable\r\n</p><p>Cable performance: up to 500 MHz\r\n</p><p>Cable Type: CAT6\r\n</p><p>Flat cable anti-tangle\r\n</p><p>Cable Jacket Material: PVC</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:34:59', '2021-11-28 11:34:59'),
(245, 255, 'D-LINK CAT6 ORIGINAL UTP CABLE 24 AWG COIL-305M FOR FULL BOX SALES', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-LINK CAT6 ORIGINAL UTP CABLE 24 AWG COIL-305M FOR FULL BOX SALES\r\n</p><p>It comply with Cat.6 specifications. This D-link product has 4-pair unshielded twisted pair (UTP) cable where pairs are braided in aluminum foil with drain wire. Owns 24 AWG solid copper conductor for superior conductivity, PE insulation, PE central cross, FR PVC/LSZH Jacket and verified compliant with EIA/TIA standards by ETLCUL-listed.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: NCB-C6UGRYR-305/INX\r\n</p><p>Model: D-Link CAT 6\r\n</p><p>Category : 4-pair unshielded twisted pair (UTP) cable\r\n</p><p>Conductor : 24 AWG (Solid)\r\n</p><p>Conductor Meta : Bare Copper\r\n</p><p>OD : 6mm ±0.2</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:38:22', '2021-11-28 11:38:22'),
(246, 256, 'Micronet CAT.6 UTP Cable 305M (Original)', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Micronet CAT.6 UTP Cable 305M (Original)\r\n</p><p>Compliant with ANSI/TIA-568-C.2, Draft 10, IEC/PAS 611565 Edition 10 class standards for Cat.6\r\n</p><p>Cat.6: Great for generation voice/data applications (Gigabit Ethernet, 155Mb/s ATM, 100 Mb/s TP-PMD/CDDI Fast Ethernet)\r\n</p><p>Cat.6: Increased usable bandwidth up to 250MHz\r\n</p><p>Standards tested: meets or exceeds current Cat.5e proposed standards\r\n</p><p>Length usage log on box: track remaining cable available for next job\r\n</p><p>FTP (Shielded twisted pair)\r\n</p><p>For Data, Voice and Video\r\n</p><p>Flame retardant rating: CM; in-wall rated; permitted in one- and two-family residential riser applications, or in riser with raceway/fireproof shaft; not permitted in plenums</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Micronet CAT.6 UTP Cable 305M\r\n</p><p>Avg. Thick.: 0.26 mm Insulation\r\n</p><p>Temp Voltage: 75°C 300V\r\n</p><p>Spark Test: 2.5 KV</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:41:12', '2021-11-28 11:41:12'),
(247, 257, 'R&M Cat 6 U/UTP Cable Box (Yellow/ Blue)', '1.0', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Connection Class\r\n</p><p>Standard\r\n</p><p>ISO/IEC 11801 2nd ed.; EN 50173-1; ANSI/TIA-568-C.2 IEC 61156-5 2nd ed.; IEC 61156-7; EN 50288-6-1\r\n</p><p>Physical Specs\r\n</p><p>Color\r\n</p><p>Yellow\r\n</p><p>Blue\r\n</p><p>Cable Details\r\n</p><p>Conductor\r\n</p><p>Bare solid copper\r\n</p><p>Insulation\r\n</p><p>HDPE, overall Ø 0.92±0.02 mm\r\n</p><p>Twisting\r\n</p><p>2 wires to the pair\r\n</p><p>Cable Lay-Up\r\n</p><p>4 pairs to the core with cross separator\r\n</p><p>Pair Screen\r\n</p><p>Non\r\n</p><p>Overall Screen\r\n</p><p>Non\r\n</p><p>Sheath\r\n</p><p>PVC, gray RAL 7035, Sheath Thickness: 0.50mm nominal\r\n</p><p>Cable Information\r\n</p><p>Application\r\n</p><p>Primary (Campus), Secondary (Riser), Tertiary (Horizontal) IEEE 802.3an: 10Base-T; 100Base-TX; 1000Base-T IEEE 802.5 16 MB; ISDN; TPDDI; ATM\r\n</p><p>Standards\r\n</p><p>ISO/IEC 11801 2nd ed.; EN 50173-1; ANSI/TIA-568-C.2 IEC 61156-5 2nd ed.; IEC 61156-7; EN 50288-6-1\r\n</p><p>Fire Rating\r\n</p><p>Flame retardant- PVC\r\n</p><p>Technical Detail\r\n</p><p>Cable Designation\r\n</p><p>U/UTP Cat.6 250MHz\r\n</p><p>Packaging\r\n</p><p>Drum 305 m\r\n</p><p>Outer Diameter\r\n</p><p>5.8±0.3mm\r\n</p><p>Weight\r\n</p><p>13.0kg nominal\r\n</p><p>Pulling Pressure\r\n</p><p>11Kg nominal\r\n</p><p>Segregation Class\r\n</p><p>B\r\n</p><p>Tensile Strength\r\n</p><p>&gt; 16.5N/mm²\r\n</p><p>Bending Radius\r\n</p><p>≥ 25 mm during operation (without load)\r\n</p><p>≥ 50 mm during installation (with load)\r\n</p><p>Temperature ange\r\n</p><p>During operation: -20°C…+ 60°C During installation: 0°C…+ 50°C</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: R795138YL\r\n</p><p>Model: Cat 6 U/UTP\r\n</p><p>Outer Jacket: FRPVC, Cable: 305M\r\n</p><p>Cable length: 305 m / 1000 ft\r\n</p><p>Twisting 2 wires to the pair\r\n</p><p>Cable lay up 4 pairs</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:44:18', '2021-11-28 11:44:18'),
(248, 258, 'D-Link CAT 6 UTP Cable 305M 23AWG Blue (Original)', '1.0', '<p>Specification:\r\n</p><p>Electrical performance: Certified channel performance in a 4-connector configuration up to\r\n</p><p>100 meters and meets ANSI/TIA-568-C.2 Category 6 and ISO\r\n</p><p>11801 Class E standards at swept frequencies up to 250MHz\r\n</p><p>Conductors/insulators: Plenum – 23 AWG solid copper covered by FEP/polyolefin insulation\r\n</p><p>Riser – 23 AWG solid copper covered by polyolefin insulation\r\n</p><p>Flame rating: Plenum – NFPA 262\r\n</p><p>Riser – UL1666\r\n</p><p>PoE compliance: Meets IEEE 802.3af and IEEE 802.3at for PoE applications\r\n</p><p>Installation tension: 25 lbf (110N) maximum\r\n</p><p>Temperature rating: 32°F to 122°F (0°C to 50°C) during installation\r\n</p><p>-4°F to 167°F (-20°C to 75°C) during operation (Riser)\r\n</p><p>-4°F to 140°F (-20°C to 60°C) during operation (Plenum)\r\n</p><p>Cable jacket: Plenum – low smoke, flame-retardant PVC\r\n</p><p>Riser – flame-retardant PVC\r\n</p><p>Cable diameter: Plenum – 0.224 in. (5.7mm) nominal\r\n</p><p>Riser – 0.210 in. (5.3mm) nominal\r\n</p><p>Cable weight: Plenum – 29 lbs./1000 ft. (13 kg/305m)\r\n</p><p>Riser – 22 lbs./1000 ft. (10 kg/305m)\r\n</p><p>Packaging: 1000 ft. (305m) in an easy payout carton\r\n</p><p>Package tested to ISTA Procedure1A</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: CB-C6UBLUR-305\r\n</p><p>Model: Panduit Cat 6 UTP Cable\r\n</p><p>23 AWG solid copper covered\r\n</p><p>Flame rating: Plenum – NFPA 262\r\n</p><p>Riser – UL1666</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:47:37', '2021-11-28 11:47:37'),
(249, 259, 'D-Link NTL-CT-001 Cable Tester (wthout Battery)', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>D-Link NTL-CT-001 Cable Tester (wthout Battery)\r\n</p><p>D-Link Cable Tester NTL-CT-001 is small hand-held device, which enables network professionals to quickly and easily authenticate Ethernet twisted pair cables. It is ideal for testing the continuity of a cable with RJ11, RJ45 or BNC connectors prior to installation. It adopts automatic scan mode which can rapidly get test result.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: NTL-CT-001\r\n</p><p>Full LED indication lights on both main and remote unit\r\n</p><p>Check RJ11, RJ45 and BNC connectors\r\n</p><p>Electricity: 25mA\r\n</p><p>Indicator: LED Lights</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:54:22', '2021-11-28 11:54:22'),
(250, 260, 'Networking Cable Tester With BNC Test (Battery Included)', '0.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Networking Cable Tester With BNC Test (Battery Included)\r\n</p><p>This Cable Tester is designed to work with various data cables and connectors\r\n</p><p>This cable tester provides a quick go/no-go reading of the wiring and connection of item under test\r\n</p><p>Tests pin configuration for 10/100 base –T, 10 base-2, RJ45 modular, AT&amp;T 258A, EIA / TIA 568A/568B cables and Token Ring cables\r\n</p><p>Checks for continuity, interruptions, short circuits or incorrect connections</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Networking Cable Tester With BNC Test\r\n</p><p>Tests pin configuration for 10/100\r\n</p><p>10 base-2, RJ45 modular\r\n</p><p>RJ45 modular</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 11:58:09', '2021-11-28 11:58:09'),
(251, 261, 'A-Grade Networking Cable Tester With BNC Test (Battery Included)', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>A-Grade Networking Cable Tester With BNC Test (Battery Included)\r\n</p><p>100% new and high quality\r\n</p><p>Main tester: 1-2-3-4-5-6-7-8-G \r\n</p><p>Remote tester: 1-4-3-2-5-6-7-8-G \r\n</p><p>able to judge the wrong connection, short circuit and Open circuit \r\n</p><p>Cable Tester for RJ12, RJ11, RJ45, Cat 5e, Cat 5, 10/100 Base-t, AT &amp; T 258 A, TIA-568A / 568B. Etc. \r\n</p><p>can be easily clarified cable, continuity, open and short. \r\n</p><p>9 LED lights for wiring connection indicated on remote and main unit \r\n</p><p>Earthing test \r\n</p><p>Structure on power switch to save energy</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Networking Cable Tester With BNC\r\n</p><p>100% new and high quality\r\n</p><p>Main tester: 1-2-3-4-5-6-7-8-G\r\n</p><p>Remote tester: 1-4-3-2-5-6-7-8-G</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:00:43', '2021-11-28 12:00:43'),
(252, 262, 'Xiaomi Mi Portable WiFi Receiver Black', '0.5', '<p>Xiaomi Mi Portable WiFi Receiver Black\r\n</p><p>The quality Xiaomi Mi Portable WiFi Receiver with 1 terabyte of cloud storage is now available at every retail outlet of Star Tech. With this Xiaomi Mini WiFi receiver you can create a portable network of free WiFi to connect your computer, laptop or mobile phone to the same local network. All we have to do is to plug Xiaomi Mini Wifi to the computer or laptop and establish a connection with a client WiFi MI. Its size is very handy to carry it in pocket just like a USB flash drive. Order online at lowest price to get this product anywhere in Bangladesh. This product has no warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Portable WiFi Receiver\r\n</p><p>Interface: USB2.0\r\n</p><p>Transmission Rate: 150Mbps\r\n</p><p>Protocol: 802.11b/n/g</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:05:44', '2021-11-28 12:05:44'),
(253, 263, 'D-Link NPP-AL1BLK241 24 Port without Modular Patch Panel', '1.0', '<p>D-Link NPP-AL1BLK241 24 without Modular Port Patch Panel\r\n</p><p>The D-Link NPP-AL1BLK241 24 Port without Modular Patch Panel is fitted with very high quality cable management bar for improved management capability and also is able to support Cat5E and Cat6 keystone jacks. The D-Link NPP-AL1BLK241 Patch Panel is able to be used with any standard 19\" rack mounts with the UL/RoHS certification. The support bar is made with SPCC, which has 1.5 mm thickness with black color paint. It can fit into both 1U and 2U patch panel. The D-Link NPP-AL1BLK241 24 Port without Modular Patch Panel has No Warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: NPP-AL1BLK241\r\n</p><p>Accepts Cat5E and Cat6 keystone jacks\r\n</p><p>UL/RoHS Certified\r\n</p><p>Cable Management Bar\r\n</p><p>Supports Standard 19” Racks</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:10:30', '2021-11-28 12:10:30'),
(254, 264, 'D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Full Loaded Patch Panel', '0.5', '<p>D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Full Loaded Patch Panel\r\n</p><p>The D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Full Loaded Patch Panel is a six Port RJ45 module. It has ID stripes for identifying port allocations and IDC which is suitable for 22-26 AWG stranded and solid wire. The D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Patch Panel is compatible with both 110 and Krone punch down tools and helps to improve cable management with optional cable management bar. The D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Patch Panel is available in 1U and 2U respectively. The D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Patch Panel has ID plate, PVC, Transparent color with paper in addition with SPCC, 1.5mm thickness with Black (RAL 9005) color painted panel. The D-Link NPP-C61BLK241 24 Port Full Loaded Patch Panel has No Warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: NPP-C61BLK241\r\n</p><p>Compatible with 110 &amp; Krone punch down tools\r\n</p><p>ID stripes\r\n</p><p>Six Port RJ45 modules\r\n</p><p>Improved Cable Management</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:13:36', '2021-11-28 12:13:36'),
(255, 265, 'R&M Cat 6 24-Port Patch Panel', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Connection Class\r\n</p><p>Standard\r\n</p><p>EN 50173-1\r\n</p><p>IEC 60603-7: Electrical Characteristics of the Telecommunication Outlets ISO/IEC 11801\r\n</p><p>Connector Class\r\n</p><p>Connection Module\r\n</p><p>Shielding Connector\r\n</p><p>Unshielded\r\n</p><p>Connector Type\r\n</p><p>RJ45\r\n</p><p>Category Connector\r\n</p><p>Cat. 6\r\n</p><p>Holder for Connector\r\n</p><p>Mounting plate\r\n</p><p>Poles\r\n</p><p>8\r\n</p><p>Physical Specs\r\n</p><p>Dimensions\r\n</p><p>18.2 mm x 22.7 mm x 41.3 mm / 0.717 in x 0.894 in x 1.626 in (W x H x D)\r\n</p><p>Color\r\n</p><p>White</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: R195498\r\n</p><p>Model: Cat 6 24-Port Patch Panel\r\n</p><p>19\" 1U 24-port metal patch panel\r\n</p><p>Rack mounting version sub-rack\r\n</p><p>4 labeling strips\r\n</p><p>Snap-in frame</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:16:23', '2021-11-28 12:16:23'),
(256, 266, 'Networking Punch Down Tool', '1.0', '<p>Networking Punch Down Tool\r\n</p><p>This is a punch down tool for putting wires into sockets, patch panels or outlets\r\n</p><p>Blades precisely insert and economically trim wire \r\n</p><p>Can be used on shielded or unshielded twisted pair cables to 110 / keystone jacks\r\n</p><p>Durable punch down tool, makes network installation all that easy\r\n</p><p>Specially designed tool for terminates and trims wires with one low-impact punch, bring new ease and speed to all of your installations \r\n</p><p>The only tool you\'ll ever need to add, change or remove connections \r\n</p><p>Universal scissors cut a variety of cable types, including 20 AWG to 26 AWG, and type 1 foam-insulated conductors \r\n</p><p>A specially-designed wire hook removes terminated conductors \r\n</p><p>A blade helps to easily remove the blocks from back mount frames</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Networking Punch Down Tool\r\n</p><p>Weight: 6.7 ounces\r\n</p><p>DIM: 10.3 x 4 x 1.4 inches\r\n</p><p>Color: Green</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:24:17', '2021-11-28 12:24:17'),
(257, 267, 'Informate HT-568R Original Crimping Tool', '0.5', '<p>Informate HT-568R Original Crimping Tool\r\n</p><p>Crimps different positions of RJ-45,RJ-11 connectors and others \r\n</p><p>Sturdy metal construction for reliability even after heavy use\r\n</p><p>This network stripping tool has comfortable contour grips\r\n</p><p>Good quality design and construction, portable &amp; compact structure\r\n</p><p>No Warranty</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: HT-568R\r\n</p><p>Crimps different positions\r\n</p><p>Good quality design\r\n</p><p>Portable &amp; compact structure</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:32:23', '2021-11-28 12:32:23'),
(258, 268, 'Crimping Tool For RJ45 & RJ11( Nonbrand)', '1.0', '<p>Crimping Tool For RJ45 &amp; RJ11( Nonbrand)\r\n</p><p>Crimp on both RJ11 and RJ45 cable connectors from a single tool \r\n</p><p>Sturdy metal construction for reliability even after heavy use\r\n</p><p>This network stripping tool has comfortable contour grips\r\n</p><p>Good quality design and construction, portable &amp; compact structure</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Crimping Tool For RJ45 &amp; RJ11\r\n</p><p>Crimp on both RJ11\r\n</p><p>cable connectors from a single tool\r\n</p><p>comfortable contour grips</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:35:02', '2021-11-28 12:35:02'),
(259, 269, 'FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine', '1.0', '<p>FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine is an Active Alignment (DAA: Digitalized Active Alignment) splicer machine. The machine has an average loss of SM(0.02dB) / MM(0.01dB) / DS(0.05dB) / NZDS(0.05dB) / G.657(0.02dB) with a splicing time of 12s average SM / SM 7s Quick mode. It has 78+ 8 user modes, User installable mode : 70+ splicing programs with attenuation range of 0.1dB ~ 20dB (0.1dB step). The fiber types that can be used in this machine are SM(ITU-T G.652, MM(ITU-T G.651), DS(ITU-T G.653), NZDS(ITU-T G.655), IT-G657A, IT-G657B, 0.25mm, 0.9mm, 2.0mm, 2.4mm, 3.0mm, FLAT(indoor cable). The average heating time is 18 second and there are 26 (Factory installed mode : 3, User installable mode : 23) heating modes that are available. The machine can store up to 2000 records. To detect the fiber, the machine uses 2 CCD camera system with Color 4.3\" LCD monitor, with Touch Screen (Tempered Glass) monitor which allows you to see all the functions and features clearly. The battery used here typical 200 Cycles (Splice &amp; Heat) / single battery &lt;2 Batteries Standard&gt; with a power supply ability of AC 100-240V input or DC 9~14V. The max wind speed resistance of this splicer machine is 15m/s.\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 4S+ Active V-Groov Clade Splicer Machine has 1 Year Warranty.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: FiberFox Mini 4S+\r\n</p><p>Smallest and the Lightest Active Alignment Fiber Fusion Splicer\r\n</p><p>SOC Compatible\r\n</p><p>Stability and Splicing Performance\r\n</p><p>Waterproof, Anti-shock, Dustproof</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:40:19', '2021-11-28 12:40:19'),
(260, 270, 'AC Net F-95 Optical Fiber ARC Fusion Splicer Machine', '1.5', '<p>AC Net F-95 Optical Fiber ARC Fusion Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The AC-Net F-95 optical fiber splicer machine has a 100% true loss report display after splicing, supports FTTH and cable TV digital system, 7800 mAh battery provides 400 nos splicing, high performance and low maintenance, suitable for rough conditions in Bangladesh. It has a 1-year warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: F-95\r\n</p><p>100% true loss report display after splicing\r\n</p><p>Supports FTTH and cable TV digital system\r\n</p><p>Splicing Capacity: 400 Nos Splicing\r\n</p><p>7800 mAh battery</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:43:43', '2021-11-28 12:43:43'),
(261, 271, 'Tumtec V9 mini Core to Core 6 Splicer Machine Tumtec V9 mini Core to Core 6 Splicer Machine Tumtec V9 mini Core to Core 6 Splicer Machine', '1.0', '<p>Tumtec V9 mini Core to Core 6 Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>V9mini uses industrial-grade Euquadrinuclear CPU (main frequency 1.4 GHz)， low power consumption；high performance, has 4.3 inch 480*272 color high-resolution capacitive touch screen， double-click can achieve 500 times the focus amplification effect, three high-power LED lights. At the same time, it has 6800 mA batteries with super endurance, 340 times more typical welding heating time, super durability, self-adaptive discharge, and automatic adjustment according to air pressure and external temperature. V9mini adopts single core alignment, six motors and fully automatic welding procedure, which brings great convenience to user\'s operation. The display can be adjusted to the optimum angle for easy operation. It runs fast with 3 seconds start-up, 6 seconds welding and 15 seconds heating. It has a 4.3 inch 480*272 color high resolution capacitive touch screen with double-click focusing more than 500 times. Users can realize the optical fiber amplification function by double-clicking the screen. Then they can observe the weld marks on the LCD screen and judge whether the weld status is good or not. The single core fiber core alignment, six motor and fully automatic welding procedure, bring great convenience to the user operation.\r\n</p><p>The Tumtec V9 mini Core to Core 6 Splicer Machine provides you with 1 Year Warranty period.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Tumtec V9 mini\r\n</p><p>Results Storage: 1000 Latest Records\r\n</p><p>Electrode Life: 3000ARCs\r\n</p><p>Splicing Length: 20-60mm\r\n</p><p>Battery Capacity: 5200mAh</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:47:26', '2021-11-28 12:47:26'),
(262, 272, 'FiberFox Mini 6SI+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine', '1.5', '<p>FiberFox Mini 6SI+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The Mini 6S+ comes with all the same excellent specification as the Mini 6s Core Alignment Fusion Splicer but with extra enhancements so that users spends even less time on each termination. This unit is still the same compact size for convenient transportation and storage &amp; comes with a full range of accessories and spares. The FiberFox Mini 6SI+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine uses the Core Alignment AOCAT(Automatic Optical Core Analysis &amp; Tracking System) method for splicing. The machine has an average loss of SM(0.02dB) / MM(0.01dB) / DS(0.04dB) / NZDS(0.04dB) / G.657(0.02dB) with a splicing time of 10s average SM / SM 7s Quick mode. It has Factory installed mode: 33, User installable mode: 70+ splicing programs with attenuation range of 0.1dB ~ 20dB (0.1dB step). The fiber types that can be used in this machine are SM(ITU-T G.652, MM(ITU-T G.651), DS(ITU-T G.653), NZDS(ITU-T G.655), IT-G657A, IT-G657B, 0.25mm, 0.9mm, 2.0mm, 2.4mm, 3.0mm, FLAT(indoor cable). The average heating time is 15 second and there are 34 (Factory installed mode : 11, User installable mode : 23) heating modes that are available. To detect the fiber, the machine uses 2 CCD camera system with Color 4.3\" LCD monitor, with Touch Screen (Tempered Glass) monitor which allows you to see all the functions and features clearly. The battery used here typical 200 Cycles (Splice &amp; Heat) / single battery, 2 Batteries Standard with a power supply ability of AC 100-240V input or DC 9-14V. The max wind speed resistance of this splicer machine is 15m/s.\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 6SI+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine has 1 Year Warranty.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Model: FiberFox Mini 6SI+\r\n</p><p>Heating Time: 15sec with 60mm sleeve\r\n</p><p>Universial Holder\r\n</p><p>LED Injection System\r\n</p><p>The Fast Splicing Time</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:50:50', '2021-11-28 12:50:50'),
(263, 273, 'FiberFox Mini 5C+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine', '1.0', '<p>FiberFox Mini 5C+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 5C+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine uses the Core Alignment DCID (Digitized Core Image Detecting) System method for splicing. The machine has an average loss of SM(0.02dB) / MM(0.01dB) / DS(0.04dB) / NZDS(0.04dB) / G.657(0.02dB). It has Factory Installed : 12 user modes, User installable mode : 128 splicing programs. The fiber types that can be used in this machine are SM(ITU-T G.652, MM(ITU-T G.651), DS(ITU-T G.653), NZDS(ITU-T G.655), IT-G657A, IT-G657B, 0.25mm, 0.9mm, 2.0mm, 2.4mm, 3.0mm, FLAT(indoor cable). The average heating time is Typical 10s (60mm sleeve) and 5 Sec (Micro Sleeve). There are 36 (Factory installed mode : 4, User installable mode : 32) heating modes that are available. To detect the fiber, the machine uses 2 CCD camera system with Color 4.3\" LCD monitor, with Touch Screen (Tempered Glass) monitor which allows you to see all the functions and features clearly. The battery used here typical 200 Cycles (Splice &amp; Heat) / single battery, 2 Batteries Standard with a power supply ability of AC 100-240V input or DC 9~14V. The max wind speed resistance of this splicer machine is 15m/s.\r\n</p><p>The FiberFox Mini 5C+ Core to Core 6 Motors Set Splicer Machine has 1 Year Warranty.</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: FiberFox Mini 5C+\r\n</p><p>Heating Time: 15sec with 60mm sleeve\r\n</p><p>Universial Holder\r\n</p><p>LED Injection System\r\n</p><p>The Fast Splicing Time</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 12:55:19', '2021-11-28 12:55:19'),
