(268, 278, 'ZKTeco F18 Access Control with Card & Finger Print', '1.0', '<p>Access Control ZK F18 Reliable, durable and highly accurate ZK fingerprint sensor with Ver. 10 algorithm provides less than 1.5 second user recognition. Works without computer. Complete setup and programming can be done via keypads and embedded firmware. Graphical user interface on a 3.5 inch TFT display for rich user experience. Audio-Visual Indication for acceptance and rejection of valid/invalid fingerprints.Relay outputs for electric lock and alarm. Inputs for door status sensor and exit switch. Supports multiple time zones and personnel groups for programming valid entry zones. The alarm will be triggered when the tamper switch is activated. Weigand output for connecting to access control panel and Ethernet port for fast and reliable communication with the computer.\r\n</p><p>Can store up to 1500 templates and 30000 transactions. The data can be backed up to a USB flash drive and can also be transferred to another reader in the absence of computer connectivity. Internal Proximity Card or Mi-fare Card reader allows dual factor authentication for access control.\r\n</p><p>Features\r\n</p><p>Three different kinds of interface style, including common, matrix and magic styles\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Reliable, durable and highly accurate ZK infrared detection fingerprint sensor with version 10.0 fingerprint algorithm\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Less than 1 second user recognition\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Stores 1500 fingerprint templates and 3000 transactions\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Reads fingerprint and/or RFID cards\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Built-in Serial and Ethernet ports\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Built-in Wiegand input/output port for connection to third part access control panels\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Built-in USB port allows for manual data transfer\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Audio-Visual indication for acceptance and rejection of valid/invalid fingers\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Tamper switch and alarm contacts\r\n</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Special Order with HID or Mifare card modules\r\n</p><p>(01 Year Warranty)</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ZK F18\r\n</p><p>Less than 1 second user recognition\r\n</p><p>Stores 3000 fingerprint templates and 30,000 transactions\r\n</p><p>Reads fingerprint and/or RFID cards.\r\n</p><p>Built-in Serial and Ethernet ports</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:24:14', '2021-11-28 13:24:14'),
(269, 279, 'ZKTeco K50A Fingerprint Time Attendance & Access Control Terminal with Adapter', '1.5', '<p>ZKTeco K50A Fingerprint Time Attendance &amp; Access Control Terminal with Adapter has Display - 2.8-Inch TFT, Fingerprint Capacity - 2000, ID Card Capacity - 1000, Logs Capacity - 80,000, Interface - TCP / IP, USB-Host, Function - Programmed Ring, SMS, Labor Code, Timetable Summer, SSR Report, Self-Service Search, Automatic Change of Status, T9 Input, 9 Digit ID, ID Card, Power Supply - 5V DC 1A, Dimension - 185 x 140 x 30mm, Additional Accessories - 31.048.01 Twinmos Patch Cord (20 Meter), 130.691.02 ZKTeco LM-1802 Electromagnetic Lock, 130.691.11 ZKTeco LM-2805 Electromagnetic Lock, 130.691.04 ZKTeco LMB-180L L Bracket, 130.691.09 Zkteco LMB-180U U Bracket, 130.691.10 ZKTeco EX-800B Exit Button (Size86L,86W, 20T(mm)), 130.197.29 Installation for Access Control.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ZKTeco K50A\r\n</p><p>Display - 2.8-Inch TFT\r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity - 2000\r\n</p><p>ID Card Capacity - 1000\r\n</p><p>Logs Capacity - 80,000</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:28:24', '2021-11-28 13:28:24'),
(270, 280, 'ZKTeco SC105 Color TFT & Graphical UI RFID Access Control Terminal', '1.5', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>ZKTeco SC105 Color TFT &amp; Graphical UI RFID Access Control Terminal\r\n</p><p>ID card Capacity-30,000\r\n</p><p>Transaction Capacity-80,000\r\n</p><p>Access Control Interface for-3rd party electric lock, door sensor, exit button, alarm, doorbell\r\n</p><p>Standard Functions- Anti-pass back\r\n</p><p>Display- TFT LCD Color Screen\r\n</p><p>01 year warranty&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ZKTeco SC105\r\n</p><p>ID card Capacity-30,000\r\n</p><p>Transaction Capacity-80,000\r\n</p><p>Standard Functions- Anti-pass back\r\n</p><p>Display- TFT LCD Color Screen</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:44:04', '2021-11-28 13:44:04'),
(271, 281, 'ZKTeco iClock 360 Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal with Adapter', '0.5', '<p>ZKTeco iClock 360 Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal with Adapter \r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity 8,000  \r\n</p><p>ID Card Capacity 10,000  \r\n</p><p>Log Capacity 2,00,000 \r\n</p><p>Display 3.5-inch Screen \r\n</p><p>TCP/IP, RS232/485, USB\r\n</p><p>(01 Year Warranty)</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ZKTeco iClock 360\r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity 8,000\r\n</p><p>ID Card Capacity 10,000\r\n</p><p>Log Capacity 2,00,000\r\n</p><p>Display 3.5-inch Screen</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:47:23', '2021-11-28 13:47:23'),
(272, 282, 'ZKTeco MB360 Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal', '1.0', '<p>ZKTeco MB360 Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal is an innovative product featured with ZK advanced fingerprint and face recognition technologies which has standard function like SMS, DTS, Scheduled-bell, Self Service Query, Automatic Status Switch, T9 Input, Photo ID, Camera, Multi-verification, 12V Output, RS232 Printer (Optional Cable). It supports multiple verification methods including face, fingerprint, card, password, combinations between them and basic access control functions. This Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal has 3rd Party Electric Lock, Exit Button, Alarm.User verification is performed in less than 1 second, which streamlines the process of access. Others feature of this Fingerprint Time Attendance Terminal are Face Capacity: 1,500 ;Fingerprint Capacity: 2,000 ,ID Card Capacity: 2,000 , Record Capacity: 100,000 , Display: 2.8-inch TFT Screen .The dimension of this terminal is 167.5x148.8x32.2 mm (Length*Width*Thickness). The communication between the MB360 and PC is by TCP / IP or USB interface for manual data transfer. Its sleek design fits perfectly in any environment.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: MB360\r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity: 2,000\r\n</p><p>Record Capacity: 100,000\r\n</p><p>Display: 2.8-inch\r\n</p><p>3rd Party Electric Lock</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:50:22', '2021-11-28 13:50:22'),
(273, 283, 'ZKTeco FR1500 Fingerprint Access Control', '1.0', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Main Features\r\n</p><p>Others\r\n</p><p>Sensor: ZKTeco Infrared Optical Sensor\r\n</p><p>Communication: RS485\r\n</p><p>Built-in Card Reader: 125 kHz EM card reader, Optional IC card reader\r\n</p><p>Optional Function: IC Card Module\r\n</p><p>Power Supply: DC 12V\r\n</p><p>Operating Temperature: 0°C ~ 45°C\r\n</p><p>Operating Humidity: 20% ~ 80%\r\n</p><p>Physical Specifications\r\n</p><p>Dimension(LxWxH)\r\n</p><p>88mm×88mm×33.6mm\r\n</p><p>Warranty Information\r\n</p><p>Warranty\r\n</p><p>1 Years</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: FR1500\r\n</p><p>Supports Password, Working with inBIO series control panels\r\n</p><p>Built-in Card 125 kHz EM card reader\r\n</p><p>Socket installation, easy operation\r\n</p><p>Built-in RFID card reader</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:53:15', '2021-11-28 13:53:15'),
(274, 284, 'ZKTeco MultiBio 800 Multi-Bio Time Attendance Terminal with Adapter', '1.0', '<p>ZKTeco MultiBio 800 Multi-Bio Time Attendance Terminal with Adapter\r\n</p><p>Face 400 \r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity 1000 Templates  \r\n</p><p>ID Card Capacity 1000 or Mifare card  \r\n</p><p>Log Capacity 1,00,000 \r\n</p><p>Display 2.8 inch TFT LCD Color Screen\r\n</p><p>RS485, TCP/IP, USB-host\r\n</p><p>01 Year Warranty</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ZKTeco MultiBio 800\r\n</p><p>Face 400\r\n</p><p>Fingerprint Capacity 1000 Templates\r\n</p><p>ID Card Capacity 1000 or Mifare card\r\n</p><p>Log Capacity 1,00,000</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:56:25', '2021-11-28 13:56:25'),
(275, 285, 'ZKTeco FR1200 Fingerprint Access Control', '1.0', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Main Features\r\n</p><p>Others\r\n</p><p>Power Supply: DC 12V\r\n</p><p>Operating Temperature: 0 ~ 45°C (32°~113°F)\r\n</p><p>Protection Grade: IP65\r\n</p><p>Communication: RS485\r\n</p><p>Physical Specifications\r\n</p><p>Dimension(LxWxH)\r\n</p><p>102 x 50 x 37mm\r\n</p><p>Warranty Information\r\n</p><p>Warranty\r\n</p><p>1 Years</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: TF1700\r\n</p><p>Works with biometric access controllers\r\n</p><p>Built-in Card 125 kHz EM card reader\r\n</p><p>IP65 rated rugged structure\r\n</p><p>RS485 Slave Reader</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 13:59:19', '2021-11-28 13:59:19'),
(276, 286, 'ZKTeco FR1300 Fingerprint Access Control', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Main Features\r\n</p><p>Others\r\n</p><p>Sensor: ZKTeco Infrared Optical Sensor\r\n</p><p>Communication: RS485\r\n</p><p>Built-in Card Reader: 125 kHz EM card reader, Optional IC card reader\r\n</p><p>Optional Function: IC Card Module\r\n</p><p>Power Supply: DC 12V\r\n</p><p>Operating Temperature: 0°C ~ 45°C\r\n</p><p>Operating Humidity: 20% ~ 80%\r\n</p><p>Physical Specifications\r\n</p><p>Dimension(LxWxH)\r\n</p><p>88mm×88mm×33.6mm\r\n</p><p>Warranty Information\r\n</p><p>Warranty\r\n</p><p>1 Years</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: FR1300\r\n</p><p>Supports Password, Working with inBIO series control panels\r\n</p><p>socket installation, easy operation\r\n</p><p>Built-in RFID card reader\r\n</p><p>Doorbell Function</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:02:27', '2021-11-28 14:02:27'),
(277, 287, 'Onspot OS930F Access Control', '1.0', '<p>Onspot OS930F Access Control\r\n</p><p>Onspot OS930F Access Control is a promotional biometric access control device. This product has Face Identification,Finger Print Access,Card and Password Excess Control verification mode.In this Onspot Access Control, it has Double camera with infrared light for accurate verification and also Wiegand in &amp; out to combine with a third party device.In this product, the Finger/Card/Password capacity is 5000, Record Capacity is 300000, Face identification capacity is 1000,  USB.TCP/IP,RS485.WiFi connector, Voice Boom,DuaI LED with 01 year of warranty.This product is Trouble free mechanism with Functional camera for using at night or low light which is fashionable and good in appearance.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Model: Onspot OS930F\r\n</p><p>Card and Password Excess Control\r\n</p><p>Face Identification\r\n</p><p>Finger Print Access\r\n</p><p>Record Capacity : 300000</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:07:15', '2021-11-28 14:07:15');
