(279, 289, 'Onspot OSF92 Access Control', '1.0', '<p>Onspot OSF92 Access Control\r\n</p><p>Onspot OSF92 Access Control is is an efficient biometric access device.This product has control mechanism of great quality for accurate fast results and suitable for all levels of enterprises with free SDK network Biometric fingerprint door access control system. It has 3000 Finger/Card/password capacity,130.000 Record Capacity, SOO DIP Fingerprint Sensor, Standalone and Network Working Mode, USB.TCP/IP.RS485WiFiWAN Remote connector, Input 26/34 &amp; Output 26/34 Threaten &amp; Unlock Wiegand. Here fingerprint and card Multiple recognition, Precise and fast operation with smart security, Weigand in and out to mixing with access controller, Trouble-free mechanism even during night by backlighted keypad, 500 Dip concealed biometric scanner for dry access, Connection with PC and server through standard IP/TCP or USB are included in this devise with 01 year of warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Onspot OSF92\r\n</p><p>Card and Password Excess Control\r\n</p><p>Finger Print Access\r\n</p><p>Record Capacity: 130.000\r\n</p><p>Finger/Card/password capacity: 3000</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:13:33', '2021-11-28 14:13:33'),
(280, 290, 'Onspot OSF93 Access Control', '0.5', '<p>Onspot OSF93 Access Control\r\n</p><p>Onspot OSF93 Access Control is biometric door access managing device which IP64 waterproof with a metal surface and suitable for both indoor and outdoor. It has multiple identification like Finger Print Access, Card and Password Excess Control where Finger/Card/Password is 5000, Record Capacity is 200000,Fingerprint Sensor is 600 DPI with USB.TCP/IP.RS485.WAN Remote connector and online &amp; offline Working Mode.it has the feature of directly control door lock also via wiegnd access controller its in directly control door lock. Standard TCP/IP. RS485. USB for communication with computer and server together with software management together for time attendance and access control. Lighted keypad for easier operation and using at night. Free SDK and Free software. This unique Access Control provides you 1 year of warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Onspot OSF93\r\n</p><p>Card and Password Excess Control\r\n</p><p>Finger Print Access\r\n</p><p>Record Capacity: 200000\r\n</p><p>Online &amp; Offline Working Mode</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:17:19', '2021-11-28 14:17:19'),
(281, 291, 'Jovision JVS-A61-XYC 1MP Indoor HD Bullet CC Camera', '0.5', '<p>Jovision JVS-A61-XYC 1MP Indoor HD Bullet CC Camera\r\n</p><p>1/4\' Megapixel high-performance CMOS        \r\n</p><p>Support AHD, TVI,CVI, CVBS output\r\n</p><p>True Day/Night        \r\n</p><p>3.6mm lens\r\n</p><p>Focus Length Board Lens 3.6mm/F2.0     \r\n</p><p>Up to 20m IR distance\r\n</p><p>Pixels 1M Pixel       \r\n</p><p>Low illumination</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Jovision JVS-A61-XYC\r\n</p><p>Sensor: 1/4\' CMOS Image Sensor\r\n</p><p>Lens: 3.6mm\r\n</p><p>IR Range: Up to 20m</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:23:57', '2021-11-28 14:23:57'),
