(284, 294, 'Jovision JVS-A73-DF Dome AHD Camerame AHD Camera', '1.0', '<p>Jovision JVS-A73-DF Dome AHD Camera\r\n</p><p>DSP &amp; Sensor  NVP2431H  +AR0130\r\n</p><p>Image Sensor 1/3\" Aptina 1.3MP CMOS Sensor\r\n</p><p>Image Resolution 1280*960\r\n</p><p>Effective  Pixels 1.3MP\r\n</p><p>TV System PAL/NTSC\r\n</p><p>Electronic  Shutter 1/25s~1/50,000s , 1/30s~1/60,000s \r\n</p><p>S/N Ratio ≥50dB   \r\n</p><p>Scanning  System Progressive   Scan\r\n</p><p>Lens Focus Length Board Lens 3.6mm/F2.0\r\n</p><p>Focus Control Fixed\r\n</p><p>Lens Type Fixed\r\n</p><p>Pixels 2M Pixels\r\n</p><p>Infrared  Distance 20M\r\n</p><p>IR  Status Under 10 Lux by CDS\r\n</p><p>IR Power On CDS Auto Control\r\n</p><p>Camera Features	Day &amp; Night Auto (ICR) / Color /   B&amp;W\r\n</p><p>OSD Menu Language N/A\r\n</p><p>White Balance Auto\r\n</p><p>Gain Control Auto\r\n</p><p>Noise Reduction	3D NR</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: JVS-A73-DF\r\n</p><p>Sensor: 1/4\' CMOS Image Sensor\r\n</p><p>Lens: 3.6mm\r\n</p><p>IR Range: Up to 20m</p>', 'en', '2021-11-28 14:32:38', '2021-11-28 14:32:38'),
