(335, 345, 'Tenda S108 10/100 8 Port Desktop Switch White', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Port\r\n</p><p>8\r\n</p><p>Data transfer rate\r\n</p><p>1.6Gbps\r\n</p><p>Description\r\n</p><p>Tenda S108 10/100 8 Port Desktop Switch White\r\n</p><p>8*10/100 Mbps auto-negotiation RJ45 ports obtains the fastest possible connection\r\n</p><p>Compliant with IEEE802.3，IEEE802.3u，IEEE802.3X standard\r\n</p><p>8* LED indicators display the connection status\r\n</p><p>Supports10/100M full duplex and half duplex\r\n</p><p>Store-and-forward forwading mode\r\n</p><p>Supports MAC address auto learning and auto aging\r\n</p><p>Supports to connect with IP-camera\r\n</p><p>Plug-and-play without configuration\r\n</p><p>Supports wall-mounting and desktop installation Energy saving technologies help you save power and money\r\n</p><p>01 Year Warranty</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Tenda S108\r\n</p><p>Backbound Bandwidth: 1.6Gbps\r\n</p><p>Access Control: CDMA/CD\r\n</p><p>MAC Address Table: 1K</p>', 'en', '2021-11-29 13:18:30', '2021-11-29 13:18:30'),
(336, 346, 'Tenda S16 16 Ports Ethernet Network Switch', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Port\r\n</p><p>16\r\n</p><p>Data transfer rate\r\n</p><p>10/100 Mbps\r\n</p><p>Description\r\n</p><p>Tenda S16 16 Ports Ethernet Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Set up a 10/100Mbps Fast Ethernet network for 16 computers in seconds, plug and play, not configuration needed\r\n</p><p>16 10/100Mbps Auto-Negotiation RJ45 ports, Supports Auto MDI / MDIX\r\n</p><p>IEEE 802.3x flow control provides reliable data transfer, support 200Mbps transmission speed at full duplex working mode\r\n</p><p>Plastic case, desktop or wall-mounting design\r\n</p><p>Plug and play, no configuration required\r\n</p><p>01 Year Warranty</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Tenda S16\r\n</p><p>Port: 16*10/100M auto-negotiation\r\n</p><p>MAC Address Table: 4K\r\n</p><p>Dimension: 218 x 135 x 41.6 mm</p>', 'en', '2021-11-29 13:21:15', '2021-11-29 13:21:15'),
(337, 347, 'Tenda SG108 8-Port Gigabit Desktop Switch', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Port\r\n</p><p>8\r\n</p><p>Data transfer rate\r\n</p><p>8* 10/100/1000Mbps auto-negotiation RJ45 ports, auto MDI/MDIX\r\n</p><p>Description\r\n</p><p>Tenda SG108 8-Port Gigabit Desktop Switch\r\n</p><p>8* 10/100/1000Mbps auto-negotiation ports\r\n</p><p>Auto MDI/MDIX simplifies networking and maintenance\r\n</p><p>Full wire speed forwarding ensures a smooth network experience\r\n</p><p>Flow control for full duplex and backpressure for half duplex avoids frame dropping as port blocked\r\n</p><p>Adopts store-and-forward mechanism and provides 4K MAC address table\r\n</p><p>9K Jumbo frame improves the forwarding speed of large data\r\n</p><p>Adopts green and environmental ABS material, improving heat resistance and heat dissipation\r\n</p><p>Allows IP camera accessing and provides a running and clear image\r\n</p><p>Desktop and wall mounting simplify installation</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: SG108\r\n</p><p>Interface: 8* 10/100/1000Mbps\r\n</p><p>Dimension: 142*90*24mm\r\n</p><p>ProtocolI: EEE 802.3/u/x/ab</p>', 'en', '2021-11-29 13:23:59', '2021-11-29 13:23:59'),
(338, 348, 'Tenda TEF1105P 5-Port with 4-Port PoE Switch', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Port\r\n</p><p>5\r\n</p><p>Data transfer rate\r\n</p><p>10/100 Mbps\r\n</p><p>Description\r\n</p><p>Tenda TEF1105P 5-Port with 4-Port PoE Switch\r\n</p><p>Compatible with All IEEE 802.3af\r\n</p><p>Automatic Detection and Protection of Non-standard Ethernet Terminals\r\n</p><p>Compact Design Fits Easily in WLAN Access\r\n</p><p>Supports 10/100 Base-T applications\r\n</p><p>Plug-and-Play no configuration required\r\n</p><p>01 Year Warranty</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Tenda TEF1105P\r\n</p><p>Interface: 4 10/100 Base\r\n</p><p>Dimension: 100 X 100 X 26mm\r\n</p><p>MAC Address Table: 2K</p>', 'en', '2021-11-29 13:26:58', '2021-11-29 13:26:58'),
(339, 349, 'Tenda TEF1024D 24-Port 10/100 Switch', '0.5', '<p>Specification\r\n</p><p>Network Switch\r\n</p><p>Port\r\n</p><p>24*10/100M Base-T Ethernet ports (Auto MDI/MDIX)\r\n</p><p>Data transfer rate\r\n</p><p>10/100Mbps\r\n</p><p>Description\r\n</p><p>Tenda TEF1024D 24-Port 10/100 Switch\r\n</p><p>The Tenda TEF1024D 24-Port 10/100 Switch is specially engineered to provide simple solution to expand 5MB networks and campus networks at the best possible cost. Connect this 24-port switch to a router and add up to twenty three more computers or other Ethernet-based devices such as a printer, Network-Attached Storage (NAS), or Internet camera to increase the functionality of your network. Housed in sturdy metal case, it is ideal for years of dependable use. The Switch contains 24 Autosensing 10/100Mbps switched ports with auto MDI/MDI-X crossover detection which provides up to 200Mbps full duplex bandwidth on each port. It is made with sturdy metal case which is ideal for years of dependable use. It has built-in 8K MAC address table with address Learning and Aging, and Data Flow Control for enhanced transmission. It can also can support 6000V lightning protection for power supply. It supports standard 13/19 inch rack-mountable which has simple Plug and Play system. The switch is solidly housed in a compact and slim metal case that is easy to position on any flat surface with limited space like desktop or mount into a rack. Plus, the device features an internal high performance switching power supply.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Tenda TEF1024D\r\n</p><p>24 Autosensing 10/100Mbps ports\r\n</p><p>Support standard 13/19 inch rack\r\n</p><p>Up to 200Mbps full duplex bandwidth\r\n</p><p>Support 6000V lightning protection</p>', 'en', '2021-11-29 13:30:23', '2021-11-29 13:30:23'),
