(635, 645, 'Deepcool GH-01 A-RGB Graphics Card Holder', '1.0', '<p>Deepcool GH-01 A-RGB Graphics Card Holder\r\n</p><p>Deepcool GH-01 A-RGB Graphics Card Holder is a gaming accessory focused around the issue of graphics card fitting in gaming builds. Most graphics cards today comes with a relatively  less bulkier size. But even so they are hard to to fit in most casings. Because most hardcore gamers today utilizes custom liquid coolers and these coolers takes up a huge space. This is where This VGA holder comes in. This Graphics card holder helps the GPU to fit in the casing and solve the space issue. this VGA holder is equipped with 9pcs of Addressable RGB LEDs. They can be synced with other 5V ADD-RGB devices by Motherboard. It is structured with the uniquely designed metal frame and plastic base, coated with premium metallic paint. apart from that the unique wire hiding function keeps the interior appearance clean and tidy while the modular designs on all the components along with hand screws makes the installation convenient and easy.It is made with reliable material with a strict manufacturing process to ensure it can easily support a heavy graphics card. The GH-01 utilizes a unique saw-tooth adjustment mechanism and a dual-hole installation design for easy installation and usage. This ARGB holder Support computer cases of different models (with or without a power supply shield). Installation of a base extension is required for cases without a power supply shield. The item dimensions are 2.39 x 6.42 x 2.07 inches. Deepcool GH-01 A-RGB Graphics Card Holder offers No warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: GH-01\r\n</p><p>9 Pieces A-RGB LED\r\n</p><p>Saw-tooth Adjustment\r\n</p><p>Unique Metal Frame\r\n</p><p>Modular Design</p>', 'en', '2021-12-07 14:18:54', '2021-12-07 14:18:54'),
