(811, 821, 'Non-brand Apple Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Description\r\n</p><p>Non-brand Apple Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>This Non-Brand Apple Mouse Pad is the optimal mouse pad for working, gaming, studying, browsing, and more. The sleek and modern design looks great on any workspace and protects a desktop from scratches. The ultra-smooth surface of this mouse pad allows for precise mouse control and can withstand heavy use. The slick surface of this mouse pad allows for quick and accurate control of your ball, optical, or laser mouse. Smoothly glide a mouse across the surface without interruption or drag. Experience enhanced control of minimal mouse movement, high-velocity movement, and mouse commands. It has no warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Non Brand Mousepad\r\n</p><p>Comfortable cloth construction\r\n</p><p>Highly stylish, Modern design\r\n</p><p>Large surface protection\r\n</p><p>Good Quality Product</p>', 'en', '2021-12-24 14:45:02', '2021-12-24 14:45:02'),
(812, 822, 'Havit HV-MP837 Gaming Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Havit HV-MP837 Gaming Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>Havit HV-MP837 Gaming Mouse Pad (Black/Red) is built in padded design to prevent injuries and wrist problems,such as carpal tunnel or cramps. For this ergonomic design, it adapts to the contour of the wrist when it is used.This Mouse Pad made for fabric gamers.\r\n</p><p>No warranty</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Havit HV-MP837\r\n</p><p>Size: 25 x 21 x 0.2cm\r\n</p><p>Ergonomic Design\r\n</p><p>Prevent injuries and wrist problems</p>', 'en', '2021-12-24 14:47:19', '2021-12-24 14:47:19'),
(813, 823, 'Hunter L16 Gaming Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Hunter L16 Gaming Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>Steady, thick, rubberized base keeps mouse pad in place and High non-slip rubber, high toughness, the same type, long life, even more firmly seize the Desktop. The diamention of the mouse pad is 30 X 23 X 0.03 cm. Gaming mouse pad are ideal for gamers, graphic designers, or anyone who uses a mouse for long sessions. This large size Mouse pad, Gaming Mouse pad, mouse pad are for pc and laptop.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Hunter L16\r\n</p><p>Steady, thick, rubberized base\r\n</p><p>A stable, comfortable base\r\n</p><p>Mouse Pad Material: Soft</p>', 'en', '2021-12-24 14:50:17', '2021-12-24 14:50:17'),
(814, 824, 'Fantech Sven MP25 Gaming Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Fantech Sven MP25 Gaming Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>Fantech MPw25 Sven Gaming Mouse Pad is one kind of GAMING Standard MOUSE PAD. Which is designed with speed type surfaces, quick and responsiveness to your mouse, build for maximum precision, Anti- slip Rubber Base, Material Rubber and 250mm x 210mm x 2mm diemension. Fabric and Rubber base is used here as materials. This gaming mouse pad has no warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Fantech Sven MP25\r\n</p><p>Quick, Eco-friendly and Responsiveness\r\n</p><p>Build for maximum precision\r\n</p><p>Anti- slip Rubber Base, Material Rubber\r\n</p><p>Size: 250mmx210mmx2mm</p>', 'en', '2021-12-25 14:16:36', '2021-12-25 14:16:36'),
(815, 825, 'Havit HV-MP846 Gaming Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Havit HV-MP846 Gaming Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>Havit HV-MP846 Gaming Mouse Pad has a premium fine-mesh cloth surface. It allows your mouse to move smoothly and accurately. It features an anti-slip rubber base that effectively keeps the mouse pad from slipping. With a size of 25 x 21x 3mm, it has a larger usable area to cover. It has an edge covering design that makes it serves much longer. The Havit HV-MP846 comes with no warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>MPN: HV-MP846\r\n</p><p>Model: MP846\r\n</p><p>Premium fine-mesh cloth surface\r\n</p><p>Mouse moves smoothly &amp; accurately\r\n</p><p>Non-Slip Rubber\r\n</p><p>Size: 25 x 21 x 3mm</p>', 'en', '2021-12-25 14:18:27', '2021-12-25 14:18:27'),
(816, 826, 'Meetion MT-PD015 Anti Slip Gaming Mouse Pad', '1.0', '<p>Meetion MT-PD015 Anti Slip Gaming Mouse Pad\r\n</p><p>The Meetion MT-PD015 Gaming Mousepad is optimized for Gaming. It is made with rubber base material. With a rough textile surface, this gaming mousepad is optimized for optical and laser gaming mice. Increase the flexibility and accuracy of printing on this gaming mousepad. The Meetion MT-PD015 has no warranty.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: MT-PD015\r\n</p><p>Optimized for Gaming\r\n</p><p>Size: 247 x 190 mm x 3mm\r\n</p><p>Rubber Base Material\r\n</p><p>Resistant to Use</p>', 'en', '2021-12-25 14:28:30', '2021-12-25 14:28:30'),
