(881, 891, 'Canon EP-326 Toner For LBP 6200 Printer (Black)', '1.0', '<p>Canon EP-326 Toner For LBP 6200 Printer (Black)\r\n</p><p>Canon Cartridge 326 Black Toner Cartridge is a replacement toner cartridge for Canon monochrome laser printers. It is manufactured in an ISO-9001 certified factory under high-quality standards that meet the specifications and performances of the OEM Canon CRG 326 toner cartridges. The compatible Canon Cartridge 326 Black Toner Cartridge delivers superb quality black text documents and sharp images and satisfies your needs for frequent printing at a low cost. With our compatible CRG 326 toner, you can print up to 2100 pages based on 5% page coverage.</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: Canon EP-326\r\n</p><p>Supported printer: LBP 6200, 6230DN Printer\r\n</p><p>Print Color: Black\r\n</p><p>Page Yield: 2,100 pages\r\n</p><p>Printing technology: Laser</p>', 'en', '2021-12-28 16:09:18', '2021-12-28 16:09:18'),
