(928, 938, 'ESET Mobile Security for Android 2021', '1.0', '<p>ESET Mobile Security for Android 2021\r\n</p><p>The ESET Mobile Security for Android 2021, ESET Mobile Security combines award-winning heuristics engine with antispam and firewall solutions to provide real-time protection against known and emerging threats, all without impacting performance. ESET Mobile Security delivers advanced anti-theft features to help protect your information, when you And, if your ever lost your device.\r\n</p><p>Antivirus for Mobile Devices\r\n</p><p>It is Built with NOD32 technology, ESET Mobile Security protects your smartphone from security breaches while you’re on the go.\r\n</p><p>Protecting more than your data\r\n</p><p>You can Automatically scans all applications installed to the phone and check third-party Android applications, files, folders and SD memory cards for malware and exploits.\r\n</p><p>SMS/MMS Antispam\r\n</p><p>It featured with SMS/MMS Antispam, so you can define trustworthy contacts via a customizable blacklist or whitelist, and also simply block unwanted text and multimedia files from unknown numbers.\r\n</p><p>Remote Lock\r\n</p><p>With Remopte Lock, you can Block the phone remotely. Its built in security system to protect your sensitive data and communications from unauthorized access in case of device loss, hacking or theft.</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\n</p>', '<p>Key Features\r\n</p><p>Model: ESET Mobile Security\r\n</p><p>SMS/MMS Antispam\r\n</p><p>Remote Lock\r\n</p><p>Proactive Anti-Theft</p>', 'en', '2022-01-08 16:24:41', '2022-01-08 16:24:41');
